      <title>Clearlake 支持的车轮制造商申请破产保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/clearlake-backed-wheel-maker-files-for-bankruptcy-protection-m0ubl8pl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wheel Pros 是一家售后专用汽车零部件制造商，由于面临通胀成本和需求下滑的困境，该公司申请破产保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/clearlake-backed-wheel-maker-files-for-bankruptcy-protection-m0ubl8pl</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OCI 以 20 亿美元的价格将甲醇业务出售给 Methanex</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/oci-sells-methanol-business-to-methanex-in-2-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OCI NV 同意以超过 20 亿美元的价格将其甲醇业务出售给 Methanex Corp.，这是这家荷兰化学品公司出售资产以提高其价值的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/oci-sells-methanol-business-to-methanex-in-2-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美的电器开始接受投资者认购，香港首次公开募股 (IPO) 规模最高可达 35 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/midea-starts-taking-orders-for-hong-kong-ipo-of-up-to-3-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美的集团股份有限公司已开始接受投资者认购，将在香港发行价值高达 35 亿美元的股票，这将成为两年来中国公司最大规模的上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/midea-starts-taking-orders-for-hong-kong-ipo-of-up-to-3-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:13:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚迷你超市连锁店 99 Speed Mart 上市首日上涨 14%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/malaysian-mini-market-chain-99-speed-mart-jumps-14-on-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[便利店连锁店 99 Speed Mart Retail Holdings Bhd 的股价在首个交易日上涨逾 14%，这是马来西亚七年来最大规模的首次公开募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/malaysian-mini-market-chain-99-speed-mart-jumps-14-on-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币升值受考验，中国经济受创抵消美联储提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/yuan-s-rally-tested-as-china-s-economic-pain-to-offset-fed-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些分析师认为，人民币近期的上涨空间有限，因为中国的经济困境可能会阻碍美联储降息后美元资产的回流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/yuan-s-rally-tested-as-china-s-economic-pain-to-offset-fed-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格自 2022 年底以来首次跌破 90 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/iron-ore-sinks-below-90-for-the-first-time-since-november-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格跌至 22 个月来的最低点 — — 跌破每吨 90 美元的门槛 — — 由于最大买家中国的需求下降导致损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/iron-ore-sinks-below-90-for-the-first-time-since-november-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:46:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称，随着经济下滑担忧加剧，亚洲股市前景恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asia-set-for-bearish-day-after-payrolls-yen-may-gain-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，由于周五美国非农就业报告差于预期，削弱了早先对美国经济软着陆的乐观情绪，亚洲股市的前景正在恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asia-set-for-bearish-day-after-payrolls-yen-may-gain-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受日元走强和美国就业数据疲软影响，日本日经 225 指数下跌 3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/japan-s-stocks-set-to-fall-on-yen-strength-soft-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市下跌，日经 225 股票平均指数下跌 3%，原因是上周日元升值，令出口商的盈利前景承压，此前令人失望的美国就业数据引发了人们对世界最大经济体健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/japan-s-stocks-set-to-fall-on-yen-strength-soft-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 22:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据加剧经济放缓担忧 股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asian-stocks-set-to-drop-after-jobs-data-fedspeak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国就业数据加剧了人们对美联储可能等待太久才降息的担忧之后，亚洲股市周一跌至三周来的最低点，日本股市领跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asian-stocks-set-to-drop-after-jobs-data-fedspeak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
